Instructions

Each node is a user in the Fandom and the edges between them are reviews

The node fill color is based on the user's first interaction in this fandom

If the user both reviewed and wrote a story then the outline of the node will be based on the type of the second interaction.

Click on a node to highlight the reviews that user left. The count of reviews sent from the selected user are displayed along the edge
